{"tid":2127755,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"糖、鹽、水嘅問題","createTime":"2020-07-27T13:14:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-27T13:56:39.000Z","uid":240342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a348362eee5008c3f13eef641e33565c84ed742b","tid":2127755,"uid":240342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T13:14:37.000Z","msg":"幾年前讀過chem，好多都唔記得，上網睇咗睇有啲嘢諗唔通<br />\n<br />\n首先講一講我目前嘅理解，希望冇錯<br />\n<br />\n「<br />\n<br />\n糖溶喺水會將糖嘅molecular chain拆開做一粒粒糖嘅molecule<br />\n<br />\n而鹽溶喺水係將鹽嘅molecule拆開成Cl-同Na+<br />\n<br />\n兩者會同水痴得埋都係因為polarity<br />\n<br />\n」<br />\n<br />\n而問題有兩個<br />\n<br />\n1. 雖然都係靠水同自己本身嘅polarity痴埋，但佢哋拆開嘅原理唔同，點解會當係同一款化學作用 (dissolve)？有冇其他名詞區別佢哋？<br />\n<br />\n2. 點解NaCl拆咗做Na+同Cl-之後仲有鹹味？"},{"pid":"4246035974c6eb8b77184be35db903578ac5bc5d","tid":2127755,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T13:19:56.000Z","msg":"首先Dissolve 只係一個統稱, 唔一定係chemical change<br />\n然後鹹味係Na+ (以及其他鹼金屬), 唔一定係NaCl"},{"pid":"fd22df00ebe10c3c422c5b18cc9b0fc60b7b1a9c","tid":2127755,"uid":240342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4246035974c6eb8b77184be35db903578ac5bc5d","tid":2127755,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T13:19:56.000Z","msg":"首先Dissolve 只係一個統稱, 唔一定係chemical change<br />\n然後鹹味係Na+ (以及其他鹼金屬), 唔一定係NaCl"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T13:22:20.000Z","msg":"所以鹽本身唔係鹹<br />\n<br />\n係拆開咗先鹹？<br />\n<br />\n明白了，射射<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d1934b6e1f279365f76da572becf51e81c6b6e8","tid":2127755,"uid":46500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd22df00ebe10c3c422c5b18cc9b0fc60b7b1a9c","tid":2127755,"uid":240342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4246035974c6eb8b77184b